        "text_GjcR9H": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Last updated: Dec 3, 2025</strong></p><p><strong>Thank you for shopping with PallyWear. Please review our shipping guidelines below.</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Order Processing Time</strong></h2><p><strong>All orders placed before 2:00 PM are processed within 1–2 business days.<br/>Orders are not shipped on Sundays or public holidays.</strong></p><p><strong>During high-volume periods, processing times may be slightly longer. If there is any unexpected delay, we will notify you by email or phone.</strong></p><h2><strong>2. Shipping Rates & Delivery Time</strong></h2><h3><strong>Domestic Shipping (India)</strong></h3><p><strong>Free shipping on all orders within India. Exact rates will be shown at checkout before payment.<br/>Delivery time varies by location and typically takes 2–5 business days after dispatch.</strong></p><h3><strong>International Shipping</strong></h3><p><strong>International shipping charges apply based on the destination country.</strong></p><p><strong>Delivery timelines depend on the courier and the importing country’s customs process.</strong></p><h2><strong>3. Shipment Confirmation & Tracking</strong></h2><p><strong>You will receive a Shipment Confirmation Email / WhatsApp message once your order has been dispatched.<br/>Tracking information will be active within 24 hours of shipment.</strong></p><h2><strong>4. Customs, Duties & Taxes (International Orders)</strong></h2><p><strong>For international shipments, customs duties or taxes (if any) are determined by the destination country.<br/>These charges are the responsibility of the customer.</strong></p><h2><strong>5. Damaged, Missing, or Wrong Items</strong></h2><p><strong>We ensure safe packaging and use trusted courier partners.<br/>If your order arrives damaged, incomplete, or incorrect, please contact us immediately at info@pallywear.com with photos or a short video.</strong></p><p><strong>✔ We will resolve the issue promptly<br/>✔ We may coordinate with the courier on your behalf<br/>✔ You do not need to contact the courier directly</strong></p><p><strong>Note: Please keep all packaging materials until the issue is resolved.</strong></p><h2><strong>6. Lost Packages</strong></h2><p><strong>If a shipment is shown as lost in transit or undelivered:</strong></p><p><strong>✔ We will assist in investigating with the courier<br/>✔ If confirmed lost, we will send a replacement or issue a refund</strong></p><p><strong>You do not have to file claims with the courier.</strong></p><h2><strong>7. Return Shipping</strong></h2><p><strong>For return eligibility and procedures, please review our Return & Refund Policy.</strong></p><h2><strong>8. Support</strong></h2><p><strong>For any delivery-related concerns, contact us at:<br/>📧 info@pallywear.com</strong></p><p><strong>We are always here to help ensure a smooth delivery experience.</strong></p><p></p><p></p>"
          }
